      children: "We offer multiple stick storage solutions integrated directly into our custom sports lockers. The most popular option is our integrated stick rack system, which attaches to the side or back of each locker, holding 2-4 sticks securely. For teams with limited space, we offer overhead stick storage systems that mount above the lockers, keeping sticks organized and easily accessible. We also design custom stick storage walls for teams that prefer centralized stick management. Our stick storage solutions accommodate all stick lengths, from youth to professional sizes, and can be customized with team colors and logos. With 30+ years of experience designing locker room lockers for hockey programs, we understand that stick storage is one of the most important considerations for hockey facilities. Our free consultation includes a complete assessment of your stick storage needs."
