      children: "Our custom wood sports lockers are built to last decades, even in the demanding environment of hockey locker rooms. With proper maintenance, our wood athletic lockers typically last 20-30 years or more, far longer than metal lockers that rust and deteriorate in high-moisture environments. The solid wood construction resists moisture damage, and our five year guarantee ensures your investment is protected. We use premium hardwoods and advanced finishing techniques specifically designed for athletic facilities. Unlike metal lockers that show wear quickly, wood lockers actually improve with age, developing a rich patina that adds character to your locker room. Our 30+ years of experience manufacturing locker room lockers for hockey programs means we understand the unique demands of ice rink environments and build our custom sports lockers accordingly."
